WEBVTT

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:13.000
Con is 11. Oof.

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:15.600
I'm going to try to sneak behind the wolves.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.900
Cunning Action to hide. Stealth check is 18.

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:21.800
If they're distracted, I'll go for a sneak attack.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.800
Shortsword out. Aiming for the big one.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.500
That's a hit. Rolling damage.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:32.500
If I see any traps, I'll try to disarm them.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.200
Staying in the shadows, moving around the edge.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:39.200
If something comes at me, Uncanny Dodge.